    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 54-57.</p><p>Legendary Smite</p><p>Also at 20th level, you learn to channel a singular oathborn strike. You can use your action and expend 1 Legendary Point to perform a Legendary Smite. Make a</p><p>— Spell Slots Per Spell Level</p><p>Prepared</p><p>— Points 1st 2nd 3rd 4th 5th 6th 7th</p><p>Divinity</p><p>Spells</p><p>1 4 16 4 3 3 3 2 1 —</p><p>2 4 17 4 3 3 3 2 1 1</p><p>3 4 17 4 3 3 3 2 1 1</p><p>single melee weapon attack against a creature within range. For this attack, the reach of your weapon is increased to 30 feet.</p><p>On a hit, the attack deals radiant damage rather than your weapon’s normal damage type. This attack does not benefit from any other bonus to its damage rolls. You can expend a spell slot alongside the Legendary Point to increase the damage of the strike, at a rate of 1d8 per spell slot level expended, as shown below.</p><p>Legendary Smite Damage</p><p>Spell Slot Expended Damage</p><p>None 3d8 x 5</p><p>1st level 4d8 x 5</p><p>2nd level 5d8 x 5</p><p>3rd level 6d8 x 5</p><p>4th level 7d8 x 5</p><p>5th level 8d8 x 5</p><p>6th level 9d8 x 5</p><p>7th level 10d8 x 5</p><p>When you score a critical hit with your Legendary Smite, you do not multiply the damage dice by 2, but instead add 2d8 to the equation.</p></div>",
      "chat": ""
    },
